title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Collection 12800
description:
PLEASE give yourself a chance - STOP ALL OTHER RUNNING TORRENTS while downloading ONLY ONE TORRENT AT A TIME FROM this series.  You know it makes sense, so just do it already ;)

Due to the fact that a single file name can contain many hundreds of files in an album format you will see artist names out of alphabetical order and the file count may be well over 300 songs.  so the number 12500 is only at best a rough guide to the total number of songs you have downloaded from me if you started at 250.

CDG+MP3 Karaoke re tagged and re file named by hand to give correct search results when playing back from a PC or MAC.  Now with multiple Karaoke Label choice on the more popular songs.

Rigmar Radio - Rockin' the free World since 1967
